@model School_Manager.Core.ViewModels.FModels.BillDto
@using School_Manager.Domain.Entities.Catalog.Enums
@using School_Manger.Extension;
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "ویرایش قبض";
    Layout = "_AdminLayout";
    var childId = ViewBag.ChildId;
}
<div class="container-fluid bg-dark text-white py-4" dir="rtl">
    <div class="card bg-dark text-white shadow-lg rounded-4 border-primary mb-4">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary bg-gradient d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <h4 class="mb-0 fw-bold">
                <i class="bi bi-pencil-square fs-4 me-2"></i>ویرایش قبض: 
                <span class="text-warning">@Model.Name</span>
            </h4>
            <form asp-action="CreateBill" method="post" class="d-inline">
                <input hidden name="ChildId" value="@childId" />
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-light fw-bold shadow-sm">
                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle me-1"></i>بازگشت
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <form asp-action="EditBill" method="post">
                <input type="hidden" name="billId" value="@Model.Id" />
                <input type="hidden" name="childId" value="@childId" />
                <input type="hidden" name="Id" value="@Model.Id" />
                <input type="hidden" name="ServiceContractRef" value="@Model.ContractId" />
                
                <div class="row g-3">
                    <!-- Bill Title -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <label class="form-label fw-bold">
                            <i class="bi bi-tag me-1"></i>عنوان قبض
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" name="Name" class="form-control bg-dark text-white border-secondary" value="@Model.Name" required />
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Total Amount -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <label class="form-label fw-bold">
                            <i class="bi bi-cash-stack me-1"></i>مبلغ کل (ریال)
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" name="Price" class="form-control bg-dark text-white border-secondary price-separator" value="@Model.TotalPrice" required />
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Payment Deadline -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <label class="form-label fw-bold">
                            <i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-1"></i>مهلت پرداخت
                        </label>
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                            <span class="text-info">
                                <i class="bi bi-clock-history me-1"></i>@Model.BillExpiredTime.ToPersianString()
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <input name="EstimateTime" class="persian-date form-control bg-dark text-white border-secondary" required />
                        <input type="hidden" value="@Model.BillExpiredTime.ToPersianString()" class="gregorian-date" />
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Bill Type -->
                   @*  <div class="col-md-6">
                        <label class="form-label fw-bold">
                            <i class="bi bi-receipt me-1"></i>نوع قبض
                        </label>
                        <select name="type" class="form-select bg-dark text-white border-secondary" required>
                            <option value="عادی" @(Model.TypeOfBill == "عادی" || Model.TypeOfBill == "نا مشخص" ? "selected" : "")>
                                <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text me-1"></i>عادی
                            </option>
                            <option value="پیش پرداخت" @(Model.TypeOfBill == "پیش پرداخت" ? "selected" : "")>
                                <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-plus me-1"></i>پیش پرداخت
                            </option>
                        </select>
                    </div> *@
                    
                    <!-- Bill Status Info -->
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="alert @(Model.HasPaid ? "alert-success" : "alert-warning") d-flex align-items-center">
                            <i class="bi @(Model.HasPaid ? "bi-check-circle-fill" : "bi-clock-history") fs-5 me-3"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>وضعیت فعلی:</strong> 
                                @if (Model.HasPaid)
                                {
                                    <span class="text-success">
                                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle me-1"></i>پرداخت شده
                                    </span>
                                    <br>
                                    <small class="text-muted">
                                        <i class="bi bi-calendar-check me-1"></i>
                                        تاریخ پرداخت: @(Model.PaidTime.HasValue ? Model.PaidTime.Value.ToPersianString() : "نامشخص")
                                    </small>
                                }
                                else
                                {
                                    <span class="text-warning">
                                        <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-1"></i>در انتظار پرداخت
                                    </span>
                                    <br>
                                    <small class="text-muted">
                                        <i class="bi bi-clock me-1"></i>
                                        مانده: @(Model.TotalPrice - Model.PaidPrice) ریال
                                    </small>
                                }
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Action Buttons -->
                    <div class="col-12 mt-4">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success fw-bold me-2 shadow-sm px-4">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle me-1"></i>ذخیره تغییرات
                        </button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-warning fw-bold shadow-sm px-4" onclick="resetForm()">
                            <i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise me-1"></i>بازنشانی
                        </button>
                        <form asp-action="DeleteBill" method="post" class="d-inline">
                            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="@Model.Id" />
                            <input type="hidden" name="secondId" value="@childId" />
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-danger fw-bold shadow-sm px-4" 
                                    onclick="return confirm('آیا از حذف این قبض مطمئن هستید؟')">
                                <i class="bi bi-trash me-1"></i>حذف قبض
                            </button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Quick Actions Card -->
    <div class="card bg-dark text-white shadow-lg rounded-4 border-info">
        <div class="card-header bg-info bg-gradient">
            <h5 class="mb-0 fw-bold">
                <i class="bi bi-lightning-charge fs-4 me-2"></i>عملیات سریع
            </h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="row g-3">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card bg-secondary text-center h-100">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="bi bi-eye fs-1 text-primary d-block mb-2"></i>
                            <h6 class="card-title">مشاهده فاکتور</h6>
                            <form asp-action="ShowBillPDF" method="get" class="d-inline">
                                <input type="hidden" name="BillId" value="@Model.Id" />
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm mt-2">
                                    <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-pdf me-1"></i>مشاهده
                                </button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card bg-secondary text-center h-100">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="bi bi-printer fs-1 text-success d-block mb-2"></i>
                            <h6 class="card-title">چاپ قبض</h6>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-success btn-sm mt-2" onclick="window.print()">
                                <i class="bi bi-printer me-1"></i>چاپ
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card bg-secondary text-center h-100">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="bi bi-copy fs-1 text-warning d-block mb-2"></i>
                            <h6 class="card-title">کپی اطلاعات</h6>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-warning btn-sm mt-2" onclick="copyBillInfo()">
                                <i class="bi bi-clipboard me-1"></i>کپی
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    <script>
        // Price separator functionality
        function formatNumberWithCommas(x) {
            if (!x) return '';
            x = x.toString().replace(/[^\d]/g, '');
            return x.replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, ",");
        }

        function unformatNumber(x) {
            return x.replace(/,/g, '');
        }

        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
            // Initialize price separator
            document.querySelectorAll('.price-separator').forEach(function(input) {
                input.addEventListener('input', function(e) {
                    var cursorPos = input.selectionStart;
                    var originalLength = input.value.length;
                    var unformatted = unformatNumber(input.value);
                    if (unformatted) {
                        input.value = formatNumberWithCommas(unformatted);
                    } else {
                        input.value = '';
                    }
                    var newLength = input.value.length;
                    input.setSelectionRange(cursorPos + (newLength - originalLength), cursorPos + (newLength - originalLength));
                });
                
                // On form submit, unformat the value
                input.form && input.form.addEventListener('submit', function() {
                    input.value = unformatNumber(input.value);
                });
            });

            // Format initial price value
            const priceInput = document.querySelector('input[name="Price"]');
            if (priceInput && priceInput.value) {
                priceInput.value = formatNumberWithCommas(priceInput.value);
            }
        });

        function resetForm() {
            if (confirm('آیا از بازنشانی فرم مطمئن هستید؟ تمام تغییرات از بین خواهد رفت.')) {
                document.querySelector('form').reset();
                
                // Reset price formatting
                const priceInput = document.querySelector('input[name="Price"]');
                if (priceInput && priceInput.defaultValue) {
                    priceInput.value = formatNumberWithCommas(priceInput.defaultValue);
                }
            }
        }

        function copyBillInfo() {
            const billInfo = {
                title: document.querySelector('input[name="Name"]').value,
                amount: document.querySelector('input[name="Price"]').value,
                dueDate: document.querySelector('input[name="EstimateTime"]').value,
                type: document.querySelector('select[name="type"]').value
            };
            
            const textToCopy = `عنوان: ${billInfo.title}\nمبلغ: ${billInfo.amount} ریال\nمهلت پرداخت: ${billInfo.dueDate}\nنوع: ${billInfo.type}`;
            
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(textToCopy).then(function() {
                // Show success message
                const originalText = event.target.innerHTML;
                event.target.innerHTML = '<i class="bi bi-check-circle me-1"></i>کپی شد!';
                event.target.classList.remove('btn-outline-warning');
                event.target.classList.add('btn-success');
                
                setTimeout(function() {
                    event.target.innerHTML = originalText;
                    event.target.classList.remove('btn-success');
                    event.target.classList.add('btn-outline-warning');
                }, 2000);
            }).catch(function(err) {
                alert('خطا در کپی اطلاعات: ' + err);
            });
        }

        // Add hover effects
        $('.btn').hover(
            function() {
                $(this).addClass('shadow');
            },
            function() {
                $(this).removeClass('shadow');
            }
        );

        // Add loading state to submit button
        $('form').on('submit', function() {
            const submitBtn = $(this).find('button[type="submit"]');
            const originalHtml = submitBtn.html();
            submitBtn.html('<i class="bi bi-hourglass-split me-1"></i>در حال ذخیره...');
            submitBtn.prop('disabled', true);
            
            setTimeout(function() {
                submitBtn.html(originalHtml);
                submitBtn.prop('disabled', false);
            }, 3000);
        });
    </script>
}

<style>
    .card {
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn {
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .alert {
        border: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .form-control, .form-select {
        border: 1px solid #495057;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .form-control:focus, .form-select:focus {
        border-color: #0d6efd;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.25);
    }

    .price-separator {
        direction: ltr;
        text-align: left;
    }

    /* Responsive design */
    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .card-body {
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        
        .btn {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .d-inline {
            display: block !important;
        }
    }
</style>